reviewText: This is best for the more advance ukulele player,  Maybe tries too much to entertain.  Perhaps more on instruction for real novices.
They were out of stock, so I believe they refunded my money.  I did not get this DVD, but I think it is okay.  I can not compare it with others and know what it has on it, since I did not get it.

Encourages you to learn chords right away. The occasional diversions between lessons are enjoyable.
A good method to learn ukulele playing in a Hawian atmosphere.
